														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-955823">
									

<p>I'm with Sorts on this too. It's a really fun article, but I just can't get into the concept as a 'serious' SCP.</p>
<p>I'm also not entirely clear how this qualifies as -EX; it's not actually explained, it's more a neutralised SCP. The article doesn't talk about how it happened. Hard to say for sure of course, since we don't have more to go on for the -EX criterion.</p>

							</div>

								
					
